{"id":892,"parent_id":890,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":892,"title":"Hosea 2","subtitle":"","short_title":"Hosea","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 2"],[".studySummary",["i","Worshipping false gods brings severe judgments upon Israel—In the last days, Israel will be reconciled to God and become His people."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.1","order":"02.29.002.60044"},["b","1"],"Say ye unto your brethren,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Ammi"],"; and to your sisters,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Ruhamah"],"."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.2","order":"02.29.002.60045"},["b","2"],"Plead with your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"mother"],", plead: for she",["i","is"],"not my wife, neither",["i","am"],"I her husband: let her therefore put away her whoredoms out of her sight, and her adulteries from between her breasts;"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.3","order":"02.29.002.60046"},["b","3"],"Lest I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"strip"],"her",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"naked"],", and set her as in the day that she was",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"born"],", and make her as a wilderness, and set her like a dry land, and slay her with",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_3d"},"thirst"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.4","order":"02.29.002.60047"},["b","4"],"And I will not have mercy upon her children; for they",["i","be"],"the children of whoredoms."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.5","order":"02.29.002.60048"},["b","5"],"For their mother hath played the harlot: she that conceived them hath done",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"shamefully"],": for she said, I will go after my lovers, that give",["i","me"],"my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"bread"],"and my water, my wool and my flax, mine oil and my drink."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.6","order":"02.29.002.60049"},["b","6"],"¶Therefore, behold, I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"hedge"],"up thy way with thorns, and make a wall, that she shall not find her paths."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.7","order":"02.29.002.60050"},["b","7"],"And she shall follow after her lovers, but she shall not overtake them; and she shall seek them, but shall not find",["i","them:"],"then shall she say, I will go and return to my first",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"husband"],"; for then",["i","was it"],"better with me than now."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.8","order":"02.29.002.60051"},["b","8"],"For she did not know that I gave her",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"corn"],", and wine, and oil, and multiplied her silver and gold,",["i","which"],"they prepared for Baal."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.9","order":"02.29.002.60052"},["b","9"],"Therefore will I return, and take away my corn in the time thereof, and my wine in the season thereof, and will recover my wool and my flax",["i","given"],"to cover her nakedness."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.10","order":"02.29.002.60053"},["b","10"],"And now will I discover her",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"lewdness"],"in the sight of her lovers, and none shall deliver her out of mine hand."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.11","order":"02.29.002.60054"},["b","11"],"I will also cause all her",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"mirth"],"to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"cease"],", her feast days, her new",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"moons"],", and her",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_11d"},"sabbaths"],", and all her",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_11e"},"solemn"],"feasts."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.12","order":"02.29.002.60055"},["b","12"],"And I will destroy her vines and her fig trees, whereof she hath said, These",["i","are"],"my rewards that my lovers have given me: and I will make them a forest, and the beasts of the field shall eat them."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.13","order":"02.29.002.60056"},["b","13"],"And I will visit upon her the days of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"Baalim"],", wherein she burned incense to them, and she decked herself with her",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"earrings"],"and her jewels, and she went after her lovers, and forgat me, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.14","order":"02.29.002.60057"},["b","14"],"¶Therefore, behold, I will allure her, and bring her into the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"wilderness"],", and speak comfortably unto her."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.15","order":"02.29.002.60058"},["b","15"],"And I will give her her vineyards from thence, and the valley of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"Achor"],"for a door of hope: and she shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"sing"],"there, as in the days of her youth, and as in the day when she came up out of the land of Egypt."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.16","order":"02.29.002.60059"},["b","16"],"And it shall be at that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"day"],", saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],",",["i","that"],"thou shalt call me",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"Ishi"],"; and shalt call me no more",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_16c"},"Baali"],"."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.17","order":"02.29.002.60060"},["b","17"],"For I will take away the names of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"Baalim"],"out of her mouth, and they shall no more be remembered by their name."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.18","order":"02.29.002.60061"},["b","18"],"And in that day will I make a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"covenant"],"for them with the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"beasts"],"of the field, and with the fowls of heaven, and",["i","with"],"the creeping things of the ground: and I will break the bow and the sword and the battle out of the earth, and will make them to lie down",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_18c"},"safely"],"."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.19","order":"02.29.002.60062"},["b","19"],"And I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"betroth"],"thee unto me for ever; yea, I will betroth thee unto me in righteousness, and in judgment, and in lovingkindness, and in mercies."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.20","order":"02.29.002.60063"},["b","20"],"I will even betroth thee unto me in faithfulness: and thou shalt",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"know"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.21","order":"02.29.002.60064"},["b","21"],"And it shall come to pass in that day, I will hear, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", I will hear the heavens, and they shall hear the earth;"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.22","order":"02.29.002.60065"},["b","22"],"And the earth shall hear the corn, and the wine, and the oil; and they shall hear Jezreel."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.23","order":"02.29.002.60066"},["b","23"],"And I will sow her unto me in the earth; and I will have mercy upon",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"her"],"that had not obtained mercy; and I will say to",["i",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"them"],"which were"],"not my",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_23c"},"people"],", Thou",["i","art"],"my",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_23d"},"people"],"; and they shall say,",["i","Thou art"],"my God."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.1a","order":"02.29.002.60067"},["b","1a"],["span.small","IE"],"My people."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.1b","order":"02.29.002.60069"},["b","1b"],["span.small","IE"],"Having obtained mercy."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.2a","order":"02.29.002.60071"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.1"},"Isa. 50:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.3a","order":"02.29.002.60073"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/13.22"},"Jer. 13:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.3b","order":"02.29.002.60075"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/16.7.7-15"},"Ezek. 16:7 (7–15)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.3c","order":"02.29.002.60077"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/16.4"},"Ezek. 16:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"3d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.3d","order":"02.29.002.60079"},["b","3d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/8.11"},"Amos 8:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.5a","order":"02.29.002.60081"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/shame"},"TG Shame"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.5b","order":"02.29.002.60083"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/44.17.15-17"},"Jer. 44:17 (15–17)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.6a","order":"02.29.002.60085"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/3.7.7-8"},"Lam. 3:7 (7–8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.7a","order":"02.29.002.60087"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/16.32.8,32,38"},"Ezek. 16:32 (8, 32, 38)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.8a","order":"02.29.002.60089"},["b","8a"],["span.small","HEB"],"grain.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/7.13"},"Deut. 7:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/16.19.17-19"},"Ezek. 16:19 (17–19)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.10a","order":"02.29.002.60091"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.8"},"Lam. 1:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.11a","order":"02.29.002.60093"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/7.34"},"Jer. 7:34"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.11b","order":"02.29.002.60095"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.8.7-11"},"Isa. 24:8 (7–11)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.11c","order":"02.29.002.60097"},["b","11c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/1.14.10-15"},"Isa. 1:14 (10–15)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.11d","order":"02.29.002.60099"},["b","11d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sabbath"},"TG Sabbath"],"."],["div",{"id":"11e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.11e","order":"02.29.002.60101"},["b","11e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.4"},"Lam. 1:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.13a","order":"02.29.002.60103"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/judg/3.7"},"Judg. 3:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/11.2"},"Hosea 11:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.13b","order":"02.29.002.60105"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.30"},"Jer. 4:30"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/23.40"},"Ezek. 23:40"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.14a","order":"02.29.002.60107"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/20.35"},"Ezek. 20:35"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.15a","order":"02.29.002.60109"},["b","15a"],["span.small","IE"],"Trouble.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/7.26"},"Josh. 7:26"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.10"},"Isa. 65:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.15b","order":"02.29.002.60111"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/15.1.1,20"},"Ex. 15:1 (1, 20)"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.16a","order":"02.29.002.60113"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/2.11"},"Isa. 2:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/52.6"},"52:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/9.16"},"Zech. 9:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.16b","order":"02.29.002.60115"},["b","16b"],["span.small","IE"],"My husband."],["div",{"id":"16c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.16c","order":"02.29.002.60117"},["b","16c"],["span.small","IE"],"My master."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.17a","order":"02.29.002.60119"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/23.13"},"Ex. 23:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.18a","order":"02.29.002.60121"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/31.33.31-34"},"Jer. 31:33 (31–34)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/5.20"},"Morm. 5:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.9"},"D&C 45:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.18b","order":"02.29.002.60123"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/job/5.23"},"Job 5:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"18c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.18c","order":"02.29.002.60125"},["b","18c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/millennium"},"TG Millennium"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/peace"},"Peace"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.19a","order":"02.29.002.60127"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/abrahamic-covenant"},"TG Abrahamic Covenant"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.20a","order":"02.29.002.60129"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/17.3"},"John 17:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.23a","order":"02.29.002.60131"},["b","23a"],["span.small","HEB"],["span.translit",["span.emphasis","lo-ruhamah."]]],["div",{"id":"23b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.23b","order":"02.29.002.60133"},["b","23b"],["span.small","HEB"],["span.translit",["span.emphasis","lo-ammi."]]],["div",{"id":"23c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.23c","order":"02.29.002.60135"},["b","23c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/9.25"},"Rom. 9:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"23d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.23d","order":"02.29.002.60137"},["b","23d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.22"},"Jer. 30:22"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/13.9"},"Zech. 13:9"],"."]]}
